description: La Piadina is a great sandwich truck serving the Fort Collins area. Offering Piadinas - authentic Italian flatbread sandwiches originally from Bologna - this truck has a little something for everyone. With homemade dough, from-scratch sauces, and a wide variety of toppings suitable for everyone from vegans to meat-eaters, all foodies are sure to find a good meal here. Check out La Piadina, and try out one of these delicious sandwiches!
name: La Piadina
